casebody.data:
Neil PARROTT, et al., Appellants,
v.
Linda H. LAMONE, et al. No. 16-588. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 9, 2017.

Motion of The Campaign Legal Center, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Appeal from the United States District Court for the District of Maryland is dismissed for want a jurisdiction.
